nodes.text: The Kesselian blockade runner was a type of military vessel manufactured or operated by inhabitants of Kessel and donated to the Rebel Alliance Fleet prior to the Battle of Endor.

Ships of this kind participated in that battle.
Captain Tessa Manchisco was surprised to find Kesselian blockade runners in the Alliance fleet upon arriving from the Virgillian Free Alignment.
